  "description": "A long forgotten sword, able to harness and manipulate the energy of ancient mobs.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Wn9XhsD/ancientvessels-title.png\" width=\"1490\" height=\"432\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/2hcK1GF/page-split.png\" width=\"1490\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/fabric-1.19.2_|_1.20.1-dddddd?style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1\" width=\"194\" height=\"28\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/install_on-client_&amp;_server-dddddd?style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1\" width=\"240\" height=\"28\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/forge-1.19.2_|_1.19.4_|_1.20.1-dddddd?style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1\" width=\"249\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/2hcK1GF/page-split.png\" width=\"1490\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<h2><strong>📘 About this mod:</strong></h2>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h4><strong>Ancient Vessels</strong>&nbsp;is an end-game weapons mod that introduces a new concept surrounding \"ancient energy\". Learn more about the legend surrounding the Ancient Vessel, discover sources of ancient energy, and fight to obtain the materials required to smith an extremely powerful sword capable of conquering the world!</h4>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/2hcK1GF/page-split.png\" width=\"1490\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<h2><strong>📖 What's inside:</strong></h2>\n<h5>&nbsp;<strong><br /></strong><strong>v1.0.0</strong> - Initial release!</h5>\n<div>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<h5>Adds five new swords: (REI highly recommended)</h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>1:</strong>&nbsp;Ancient Vessel (Attack: 6 | Attack Speed: 1.4)</h5>\n<h5>Crafting recipes:<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/YRWTDT3/ancientvessels-smithing-draconic-vessel-1.png\" width=\"408\" height=\"98\" /></h5>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/QpB9wRK/ancientvessels-smithing-decayed-vessel-1.png\" width=\"408\" height=\"98\" /></p>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>2:</strong>&nbsp;Draconic Vessel (Attack: 7 to 8 | Attack Speed: 1.4)</h5>\n<h5>Crafting recipes:<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/jyyH4YR/ancientvessels-smithing-draconic-vessel-2.png\" width=\"408\" height=\"98\" /></h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>3:</strong> Decayed Vessel (Attack: 7 to 8 | Attack Speed: 1.4)</h5>\n<h5>Crafting recipes:<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/pwMB1fy/ancientvessels-smithing-decayed-vessel-2.png\" width=\"408\" height=\"98\" /></h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>4:</strong>&nbsp;Dragon Vessel (Attack: 10 | Attack Speed: 1.4)</h5>\n<h5>Crafting recipes:<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1Kt0LB6/ancientvessels-smithing-dragon-vessel.png\" width=\"408\" height=\"98\" /></h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>5:</strong>&nbsp;Wither Vessel (Attack: 10 | Attack Speed: 1.4)</h5>\n<h5>Crafting recipes:<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/ftP5k8Y/ancientvessels-smithing-wither-vessel.png\" width=\"408\" height=\"98\" /></h5>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/2hcK1GF/page-split.png\" width=\"1490\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<h2><strong>🙋&zwj;♂️ FAQ:</strong></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><strong>Q: Will you backport to any older versions?&nbsp;</strong></h5>\n<h5><strong>A:</strong> No. I prefer to keep my attention on the latest versions.&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>Q: Does this work on version ____?</strong></h5>\n<h5><strong>A:</strong> Try it and see! If it does, please comment so I can mark it.&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>Q: Is the Forge version really a beta?</strong></h5>\n<h5><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;No. I mark the Fabric versions as 🟩Release, and the Forge versions as 🟦Beta. I won't upload a beta release here.&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h5>\n<h5><strong>Q: I'm a little lost, and there's no wiki. How do I progress?</strong></h5>\n<h5><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;Progression is mostly tracked in the Advancements tab. Hint: These are end-game weapons... you must beat the game first.</h5>\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5><strong>Q: This mod feels a bit overpowered/underpowered. Is there a config?</strong></h5>\n<h5><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;There is no config at this time. As I am relatively new to mod making, creating a config that works with Fabric and Forge is quite difficult. I'm hopeful in the future, there will be a config. If you have comments about this mod, please join the <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/X6AsDnqex6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Discord</a> and share your thoughts.&nbsp;</h5>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/2hcK1GF/page-split.png\" width=\"1490\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Leave a comment!</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Thanks for downloading!</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">😅💗</h2>\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/purejoshmods/membership\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/buy_me_a_coffee-if_you_appreciate_my_work-dddddd?style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1&amp;logo=buymeacoffee&amp;logoColor=000000\" width=\"540\" height=\"40\" /></a></h2>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/X6AsDnqex6\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1006811832897519686?color=dddddd&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=black\" width=\"193\" height=\"32\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/purejoshmc/projects\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/curseforge-purejoshmc-dddddd?style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=black\" width=\"269\" height=\"32\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/purejosh\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/github-purejosh-dddddd?style=for-the-badge&amp;labelColor=aaf0d1&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=black\" width=\"207\" height=\"32\" /></a></p>",
